narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned the necessary skills to be a better musician and received specific instruction to help improve my personal playing.
Improved performance and musical skills -- finding characters in the pieces.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This course could be best improved by having later, better publicized auditions. Lots of people miss out auditioning at the beginning of the year because the course isn't widely advertised.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would recommend lessons for any undergraduate musicians who want to improve on their playing during college.
This course was excellent. You can grow immensely as a musician through this training -- it's the best way to improve your classical voice at Yale.
